The secret gate
The magical artifact that the great mage Tka-Rick spoke of should be found in a cave beyond the Ice Desert. At least that's what Jam-Akara is sure of.
#subobj 1
Go to the cave entrance
The cave entrance is located in the west of the Ice Desert.
#subobj 2
Open the entrance!
To open the entrance you need to use the key that the Clever Man made.